<!-- Page Hero -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container page-hero-content">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p>Answers to common questions about our services and products.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Content -->
<section style="background-color:var(--background);padding:5rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:50rem;margin:0 auto;" class="faq-list">

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What areas do you service?</summary>
        <p>We service all five boroughs of New York City (Brooklyn, Manhattan, Queens, Bronx, Staten Island),
           as well as New Jersey and Connecticut. Our main offices are located in Brooklyn, NY and Marlboro, NJ.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How quickly can you respond to service calls?</summary>
        <p>We are committed to responding to all service requests within 24 hours. For emergencies,
           we offer same-day service when possible. Call us at 718-259-1842 for urgent situations.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How often should beer lines be cleaned?</summary>
        <p>Industry standards recommend cleaning beer lines every two weeks for optimal beer quality and
           hygiene. We offer regular line cleaning service contracts to ensure your systems are always
           compliant and serving the best product possible.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you sell both new and used equipment?</summary>
        <p>Yes! We sell both new and used soda fountains, bar guns, beer taps, draft systems,
           and other beverage equipment. Used equipment can be a great cost-effective option for
           businesses on a budget.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can you design a custom draft beer system?</summary>
        <p>Absolutely. Whether it's a single kegerator or a multi-tier draft beer system, our experts
           can design and install a system from the ground up tailored to your specific space and needs.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you offer maintenance contracts?</summary>
        <p>Yes, we offer preventive maintenance contracts that include regular inspections, cleaning,
           and tune-ups. These contracts help extend equipment life and prevent costly breakdowns,
           saving you money in the long run.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What types of compressed gas do you supply?</summary>
        <p>We supply CO2, G-Mix, Beer Gas, Nitrogen, and Helium for all commercial applications.
           Contact us for pricing and delivery information.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Are your products kosher?</summary>
        <p>Yes! Roma Syrups is proud to sell kosher-certified products. Please contact us for
           more details on our kosher product offerings.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you service home soda dispensers?</summary>
        <p>Yes, we service home soda dispensers and soda fountains in addition to our commercial
           services. Contact us to schedule a service appointment.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How can I request a free consultation?</summary>
        <p>You can request a free consultation by calling us at
           <a href="tel:718-259-1842" style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;">718-259-1842</a>,
           emailing us at
           <a href="mailto:info@romasyrups.com" style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;">info@romasyrups.com</a>,
           or filling out the
           <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;">contact form</a> on our website.
           We respond within 24 hours.
        </p>
      </details>

    </div><!-- /.faq-list -->
  </div><!-- /.container -->
</section>

<style>
  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--card);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--foreground);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '−'; }

  .faq-item summary:hover { background-color: var(--secondary-bg); }

  .faq-item[open] summary {
    background-color: var(--secondary-bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .faq-item p {
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted-fg);
  }
</style>

